Code.Terraform:
```hcl
# Terraform：将 viewer_protocol_policy 设置为强制 HTTPS
resource "aws_cloudfront_distribution" "<example_resource_name>" {
  default_cache_behavior {
    target_origin_id       = "<example_origin_id>"
    viewer_protocol_policy = "redirect-to-https" # 关键：强制 HTTP 重定向到 HTTPS
  }
}
```
